target.mrk: The fixing ring is used to mounting the <MadCap:variable name="ModuleAndDevicesNames.MCScap-E_name" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> electrodes to the <MadCap:variable name="ModuleAndDevicesNames._mainMCScap" xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" /> textile cap.
The rings have a groove to fit into the holes of the cap, which allows you to replace or install additional rings on the cap.
